headline: 3 Reasons STX is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: In a sliding market, Seagate Technology has defied the odds, trading up to $123.86 per share. Its 26.9% gain since December 2024 has outpaced the S&P 500’s 1.9% drop. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
